==English==
===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[reducere]]'', to bring back

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ˈridʌks/

===Adjective===
'''redux'''
#Of a [[topic]], restored, brought back, [[revisit]]ed
#:''Company policy redux''

====Usage notes====
*'''Redux''' is always used [[attributively]] and after the noun rather than before it.